{"tid":1512664,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港自由之書——報應來了，街站收集投訴信(偽)","createTime":"2019-08-28T03:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T09:38:12.000Z","uid":208452,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"45828885931e51c7a7ea3096a9c3a03adf78d1f6","tid":1512664,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:36:00.000Z","msg":"對上一個POST出錯日期, 決定重開<br />\n<br />\n原POST:<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1510955/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1510955/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n對上兩次荃灣店同旺中店賣卡撲水投資國難五金,<br />\n可怕投資連連虧損, 我地收到唔少市民的怨言<br />\n所以我地決定回到最初的起點&mdash;&mdash;旺角東天橋<br />\n收集市民的投訴同不滿！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n活動詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n活動名: 寄信投訴奸商活動<br />\n日期:<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">8月28日 - 8月29日</span></span><br />\n時間:5pm-10pm<br />\n地點:旺角東天橋 連濃牆位置（近MOKO出口)<br />\n奸商P&amp;M義工到時會派發信封比<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大家中意放咩就放咩 </span></span><br />\n交完信我地會派埋卡 未知magic 定ptcg<br />\n我地係唔會睇放左咩 直到回總部前<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 大家中意放咩都得 </span></span><br />\n呢個星期奸商搵幾多 <br />\n一部分投資<span style=\"color: red;\">國難五金 </span><br />\n一部分幫助既某些手足生活同醫療費用<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地亦歡迎各位封好信封直接交比我地</span><br />\n<br />\n唔方便落黎的可以繼續過數訂卡:<br />\n<br />\n銀行戶口: 015-256-68-02365-9 (東亞銀行)/FPS<br />\n<br />\nFPS識別碼: 3618246<br />\n<br />\nPM TECHNOLOGY LTD<br />\n<br />\n另外人手同街站安全問題,唔會接收任何玩具同文具或其他物資,<br />\n如有問題, 或者有玩具想比我地前 請先FB/TG聯絡我地<br />\n<br />\n義工一號: <a href=\"https://t.me/codingnoob\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcodingnoob&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=c91e8f5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/codingnoob</a><br />\n<br />\n義工二號: <a href=\"https://t.me/fightforh_k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffightforh_k&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=129d7da3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/fightforh_k</a><br />\n<br />\nFB PAGE: 香港自由之書<br />\nTG Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=76839fe9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另設海外訂卡渠道<br />\nPaypal: freemyhk@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望呢兩日見到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n831不見不散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外書個到預計年底會出到世<br />\n【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"90fc085fe04a978cad9cfcebbf984989516ea773","tid":1512664,"uid":284522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T03:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=b2d7d1a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=zAhFImnUcMh%2FonyB55KWQ%2BSm5IdDY